{"tid":1758382,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[方向唔會報的新聞]因管理得善而在全球最佳航空公司排名榜節節上升的國泰航空","createTime":"2019-11-27T04:29:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T04:44:07.000Z","uid":275570,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"458eccaf7762277b2f3cf58007a75979af2913df","tid":1758382,"uid":275570,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:29:25.000Z","msg":"HKET<br />\n<br />\n2020年全球十大航空排名 國泰排第五 新西蘭航空重奪第一<br />\n<br />\n環球經濟金融 16:24 2019/11/26<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://國際航空專業評鑑網站AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E5%B0%88%E6%A5%AD%E8%A9%95%E9%91%91%E7%B6%B2%E7%AB%99AirlineRatings.com&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=9214f809\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">國際航空專業評鑑網站AirlineRatings.com</a>公布2020年全球十大航空公司排名，新西蘭航空（Air New Zealand）擊敗去年冠軍新加坡航空（Singapore Airlines），重上首位，第六度獲此殊榮。國泰航空（Cathay Pacific Airways）排名第五，較2019年的排名上升4位。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭航空重奪全球最佳航空 SkyCouch值回票價？<br />\n2020年全球十大航空公司首五名<br />\n1  新西蘭航空<br />\n2  新加坡航空<br />\n3  全日本航空<br />\n4  澳洲航空<br />\n5  國泰航空<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=0e56db99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>稱，屢獲殊榮的新西蘭航空憑創紀錄的性能、機上創新技術、飛行安全、環保領先及員工積極性，令該航空公司攀上行業之最。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://AirlineRatings.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FAirlineRatings.com&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=0e56db99\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">AirlineRatings.com</a>「卓越航空公司獎」（Airline Excellence Awards）會根據12項準則評選，包括機齡、旅客評價、盈利能力、投資評級等，選出2020年度最佳航空公司。總編輯托馬斯（Geoffrey Thomas）指，新西蘭航空在大多數審核標準中均排第一。<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭航空早前推出SkyCouch座位服務。 ▲ 新西蘭航空早前推出SkyCouch座位服務。<br />\n<br />\n航空公司大削飛往香港航班 報道稱反修例示威愈來愈激烈<br />\n<br />\n全球最佳機場＋航空公司 今年由一地包辦 香港榜上無名<br />\n<br />\n新西蘭航空早前推出SkyCouch座位服務，只要兩人購買2個經濟客艙座位，即可以半價購買同行的第三個座位，把整行座位打通，自製飛機上的梳化床。<br />\n<br />\n國泰航空以往曾位列三甲，但在2017年跌至第四位，2018年及2019年排第九位。<br />\n<br />\n記者：鄧燕君<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2506329/2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%20%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%20%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%A5%AA%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2506329%2F2020%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E5%258D%2581%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%258E%2592%25E5%2590%258D%2520%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%25B3%25B0%25E6%258E%2592%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25BA%2594%2520%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%2598%25AD%25E8%2588%25AA%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E9%2587%258D%25E5%25A5%25AA%25E7%25AC%25AC%25E4%25B8%2580&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRGg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=a8dc0d76\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2506329/2020%E5%B9%B4%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%A7%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%8E%92%E5%90%8D%20%E5%9C%8B%E6%B3%B0%E6%8E%92%E7%AC%AC%E4%BA%94%20%E6%96%B0%E8%A5%BF%E8%98%AD%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E9%87%8D%E5%A5%AA%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80</a>"},{"pid":"c74acbf91d5f11e67916f6c3ae6cfc7b9a790e5a","tid":1758382,"uid":231933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:31:56.000Z","msg":"第五，暗指五大訴求！"},{"pid":"48a22b364d08de45e5c08f09afca031f903c5cb2","tid":1758382,"uid":273825,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:35:30.000Z","msg":"垃圾奶共因航<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fc51bbbfde0710015bd9de1ab02270ab37ad358","tid":1758382,"uid":61985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T04:40:24.000Z","msg":"hknewsurl<br />\n一站式 香港新聞整合與listing<br />\ntelegram bot: <a href=\"https://t.me/newshk_bot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnewshk_bot&d=CdC2hxDFSK2eX8E0jz8mRG